[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0684","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0684.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0891","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Download Behavior 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 的下载行为（Download Behavior）功能存在安全漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造特制的服务端重定向（server-side redirect）响应，诱使用户访问恶意网页后绕过 IE 5 的安全限制，实现跨域读取目标系统上的任意文件。该漏洞影响 Internet Explorer 5 版本，攻击成功的前提是受害者使用受影响浏览器访问攻击者控制的恶意站点，无需额外认证，可能导致敏感信息泄露。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0891"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:16.310","remediation":"立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.5 以上版本，该漏洞在 IE 5.5 及后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，建议禁用 ActiveX 控件及脚本下载行为：在 Internet 选项 → 安全 → 自定义级别中，将\"下载已签名的 ActiveX 控件\"和\"下载未签名的 ActiveX 控件\"均设为\"禁用\"。根本解决措施是停止使用已停止支持的 Internet Explorer，迁移至 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ242542","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-002.shtml","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/37828","http://www.osvdb.org/11274","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/674","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-040","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19530"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0684.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0970","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1129","title":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 VLAN交换机 未授权VLAN遍历漏洞","description":"Cisco Catalyst 2900 系列虚拟局域网交换机中存在 IEEE 802.1q VLAN 遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过伪造中继标签中的 VLAN 标识符，向其他 VLAN 注入 802.1q 帧，从而打破 VLAN 隔离机制实现跨 VLAN 访问。该漏洞允许攻击者无需认证即可绕过网络隔离策略，窃取或篡改不同 VLAN 中的敏感数据。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1129"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:46.940","remediation":"将所有非 trunk 端口设为静态 access 模式（`switchport mode access`），禁用 DTP（`switchport nonegotiate`），并在 trunk 端口上启用 VLAN 修剪（`vlan pruning`）以及限制允许的 VLAN 列表（`allowed vlan`）。同时配置本征 VLAN 为未使用的专用 ID 并关闭自动协商。这些措施可阻断伪造 802.1q 帧跨 VLAN 攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.cisco.com/univercd/cc/td/doc/product/lan/28201900/1928v8x/eescg8x/aleakyv.htm","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/26008","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/615","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3294","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/92d64b4c9b3c5a0ce1fd1e5f8c017b9772e0139b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1129","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1129.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/db45dbc75ff0264d63b603291e4a83d7361bd7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/79c2cf4630fcc44f2632735de08432a07cfaf204/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-29q9-4h2h-9p7g/GHSA-29q9-4h2h-9p7g.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/615/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1129.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--ecbfddda-04a3-4138-b1cd-3892ec7d91fd.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--ecbfddda-04a3-4138-b1cd-3892ec7d91fd.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0970.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0503","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0503.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0774","title":"Martin Stover Mars NWE 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Mars NetWare Emulation (NWE, mars_nwe) 软件包中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向目标系统提交超长目录名触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，进而实现本地权限提升或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Martin Stover Mars NWE 0.99 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0774"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.833","remediation":"立即卸载 mars_nwe 软件包（apt-get remove mars_nwe），该软件已停止维护多年且已从 Debian 仓库移除。迁移至其他受支持的 NetWare 兼容解决方案（如使用 Samba 替代文件共享服务）。如暂时无法卸载，严格限制本地登录用户为受信任账户，并通过 iptables 限制对 524/TCP 和 524/UDP 端口的访问以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/617","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19485"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0503.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1145","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1145.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1515","title":"TenFour TFS Gateway 4.0 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"TenFour TFS Gateway 4.0 在非默认配置下存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过发送包含错误发件人和收件人地址的邮件消息，导致网关每 10 秒持续尝试返回该消息，形成处理循环，大量消耗系统资源，造成邮件服务不可用。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。受影响版本为 TenFour TFS Gateway 4.0，建议升级或修复地址验证逻辑。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1515"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-31T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.357","remediation":"TenFour TFS Gateway 4.0 已停止维护，厂商不再提供安全更新。建议立即升级至不受影响的替代产品或迁移至其他网关方案；如无法升级，应避免启用非默认的地址验证绕过配置，并在防火墙上限制对网关服务的非必要访问。临时缓解措施可配置消息队列超时策略，防止无效地址消息导致持续重试造成资源耗尽。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/613","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3290","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19477","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1515.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1515","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1515.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1515.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/72e1ca263be82e97277404223a060b794df013c9/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-68q7-2qpc-87mh/GHSA-68q7-2qpc-87mh.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/613/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1515.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1145.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1071","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1071.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1354","title":"Softarc FirstClass Internet Server 敏感信息明文存储漏洞","description":"Softarc FirstClass Internet Server 5.506 及更早版本中的 E-mail 客户端存在明文存储敏感信息的漏洞。服务器将用户账号和密码以明文形式保存在本地文件中，包括 5.506 版的 home.fc、3.5 版的 network.fc 以及启用日志时的 FCCLIENT.LOG 文件。本地攻击者若能访问这些文件，即可直接获取用户的凭证信息，进而冒充目标用户登录系统。该漏洞源于程序未对存储的敏感数据进行加密处理。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1354"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.720","remediation":"升级 Softarc FirstClass Internet Server 至 5.506 以上版本。禁用调试日志功能以防止 FCCLIENT.LOG 记录明文凭据。通过文件系统 ACL 严格限制 home.fc、network.fc 和 FCCLIENT.LOG 的访问权限，仅允许必要系统账户读取。若厂商已停止支持，建议迁移至继续维护的邮件服务软件（如 Microsoft Exchange 或 Dovecot）以避免凭据泄露风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93637687305327&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93698283309513&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1354.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1354","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1354.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a75ebb477762f54f32c38d85ec939339ec2712e5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1354.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vm2r-v9g5-m7v4/GHSA-vm2r-v9g5-m7v4.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1354.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000754.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--80742b1f-750a-4cc5-b3e9-d6215f20b69b.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1071.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1143","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1143.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1513","title":"3Com SuperStack II hub MIB信息泄露漏洞","description":"3Com SuperStack II 集线器运行软件版本 2.10 中的管理信息库（MIB）存在信息泄露漏洞。该 MIB 包含一个对象标识符（.1.3.6.1.4.1.43.10.4.2），通过只读 community 字符串即可访问，但该对象会泄露完整的 community 字符串表，包括读写权限的 community 字符串。攻击者可在未授权情况下通过 SNMP 协议读取该 OID，获取高权限 community 字符串后进一步执行设备配置篡改、信息窃取等未授权操作，严重威胁网络设备安全。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1513"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-30T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:36.093","remediation":"升级 3Com SuperStack II hub 固件至 2.10 以上版本，并在设备 ACL 中限制 SNMP 仅允许受信管理 IP 段访问，同时将 SNMP 读团体字串由默认的 public 改为复杂随机字符串，禁用不必要的 SNMP 服务或使用 SNMPv3 加密认证。如设备已停产，应替换为支持安全 SNMP 的现代设备。最终，建议加固方式是在网络边界防火墙封禁 UDP 161/162 端口的外部访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93616983223090&w=2","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ea7161c86d011c8f810b70db6eb52fc6fcb9878b/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1513.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1513","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1513.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bc69cd1e5221f68ef56bd10c5c61adf76a19f0fc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1513.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/44d84714e9a3b4364d62f8189e2d74dba61b570e/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gwm8-rgj9-362f/GHSA-gwm8-rgj9-362f.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1513.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87920/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/8200d63179d89b9076027cd96356d55ef8a5349e/1999.tsv","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1143.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0866","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1016","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer HTML Form Control 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 及 FrontPage Express、Outlook Express 5、Eudora 等软件所使用的 HTML Form Control 组件存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过构造包含超大表单输入字段（如表格单元格中的大量文本框）的恶意网页或 HTML 邮件，诱使用户访问后导致目标系统 CPU 占用率高达 100%，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需认证即可触发，影响范围广泛。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1016"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.717","remediation":"升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本可修复此漏洞。对于仍使用旧版 IE 的环境，建议禁用 Active Scripting 及在 Outlook Express 中阻止 HTML 邮件加载表单控件。现网用户应迁移至受支持的现代浏览器（如 Edge、Chrome）以免受此及其他已知漏洞影响。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=93578772920970&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/606","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19471","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1016.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1016","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/xaitax/SploitScan/blob/e7c7a6140bbd6a60ea622b6124620fbed9d12332/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1016.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-33jr-59q9-j8vq/GHSA-33jr-59q9-j8vq.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/smb_nt_ms02-005.nasl","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1016.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0866.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0866.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1209","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0911","title":"ProFTPd MKD/CWD 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ProFTPd 1.2 pre1 至 pre5 版本、wu-ftpd 及 beroftpd 中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送一系列精心构造的 MKD（创建目录）和 CWD（切换目录）命令，创建深层嵌套目录结构，触发缓冲区溢出，进而获得 root 权限。该漏洞影响多个主流 FTP 服务端软件，危害严重，无需认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0911"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.797","remediation":"升级 ProFTPd 至 1.2.0 RC1 或更高稳定版本（1.2.0pre 系列已停止支持），该漏洞在 1.2.0 RC1 中修复。使用 wu-ftpd 的用户应升级至 2.6.2 或更新版本，或在 inetd 配置中禁用匿名用户 MKD/CWD 目录创建权限作为临时缓解措施。beroftpd 用户建议迁移至已维护的 FTP 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.debian.org/security/1999/19990210","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/612","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19476"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0736","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0736.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0939","title":"Debian Linux epic/epic4 IRC客户端 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Debian Linux 2.1 和 2.2 版本中附带的 epic/epic4 IRC 客户端存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向客户端发送特制的超长字符串，触发客户端崩溃或无法响应，导致正常的 IRC 通信服务中断。该漏洞无需认证即可利用，攻击复杂度低，虽未造成数据泄露或代码执行，但严重影响服务的可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0939"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.163","remediation":"升级 epic4 到 2.8 以上版本（Debian 2.1/2.2 已 EOL，建议升级到 Debian 3.0 Woody 或更新版本，其中包含已修复的 epic4 包）；也可改用 irssi、weechat 等替代 IRC 客户端，或在 IRC 服务器端限制单条消息最大长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/605"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0736.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0483","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0768","title":"Red Hat Linux Vixie Cron MAILTO 环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 是 Linux 系统中广泛使用的任务调度程序。RedHat Linux 4.2/5.2/6.0 及 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.0/6.1 版本中，Vixie Cron 在处理 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长 MAILTO 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码，完全控制目标系统。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击者需拥有本地账户权限方可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0768"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.067","remediation":"升级 Vixie Cron 至 3.0.1 或更高版本，或安装对应发行版安全补丁（Red Hat 6.2+ 已修复）。如无法升级，在 crontab 中避免使用 MAILTO 变量，或限制 crontab 文件权限为 600 并仅允许受信用户编辑。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/602","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19470","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0768.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0768","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0768.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1d279cde1e5f7d9e150ca373126c9b35476ad3f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0768.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q395-vm9c-r75g/GHSA-q395-vm9c-r75g.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0768.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0483.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0489","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0769","title":"Linux Vixie Cron MAILTO 环境变量本地命令注入漏洞","description":"Vixie Cron 是 Linux 系统中广泛使用的任务调度程序，其 MAILTO 环境变量在处理 cron 任务输出时存在参数注入漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 crontab 中设置特制的 MAILTO 变量值，向 sendmail 命令注入额外参数，从而以 root 权限执行任意命令或操纵邮件发送行为。该漏洞影响 Caldera OpenLinux 2.2、Debian 2.1/2.2、RedHat 6.0 等发行版，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限以创建或修改 crontab 条目，利用条件相对有限但危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0769"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.193","remediation":"升级 Vixie Cron 至 3.0pl1-55 或更高版本，该版本修复了 MAILTO 环境变量注入问题。对于 Debian 系统，安装 cron 包更新至 3.0pl1-57+；对于 RedHat 系统，应用 RHSA-1999:026 提供的补丁。如无法升级，可在 crontab 中避免使用 MAILTO 变量，或限制 crontab 文件仅允许 root 用户修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19474","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e6863af1ae3bb1cd8c56c1f1aac61d836661ac74/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0769.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0769","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0769.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/dabf5b9888e8885cf125c5729901a7ad84d00092/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0769.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9qf9-2h54-chr8/GHSA-9qf9-2h54-chr8.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/debiancn/debian.org/blob/6abc98daa6356b20e410013a6920b3764af682d4/english/security/1999/19990830.data","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0769.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--96d6bfc3-3242-4258-a570-581568f1a763.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0489.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0489.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0489.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0669","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0669.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0872","title":"Vixie Cron 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Vixie cron 在处理 crontab 文件中的 MAILTO 环境变量时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可创建包含超长 MAILTO 字符串的特制 crontab 文件触发溢出，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 OpenLinux 等多种 Linux 发行版中的 Vixie cron 服务，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限即可利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0872"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:13.990","remediation":"升级 Vixie cron 至 3.0pl1 或更高版本，该版本已限制 crontab 中 MAILTO 环境变量的最大长度，防止缓冲区溢出导致权限提升。如无法立即升级，可暂时移除 crontab 文件中所有 MAILTO 赋值语句作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/611","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/759"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0669.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1018","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1018.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1235","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 FTP 密码信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 存在 FTP 凭据泄露漏洞。当用户通过 FTP 协议访问服务器时，程序将用户名和密码以明文形式记录在浏览器历史记录（index.dat）中，未进行任何加密或脱敏处理。本地攻击者可读取其他用户的 index.dat 文件，从中提取 FTP 账户信息；物理接近的攻击者也可通过肩窥方式，在用户鼠标悬停于 FTP 链接时从浏览器状态栏直接获取凭据。该漏洞影响 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1235"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-25T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.410","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本可缓解密码明文记录问题；根本解决方案是使用专用 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla）替代 IE 访问 FTP 站点，并避免在 URL 历史中保留密码。使用后建议及时清除 IE 历史记录，并对敏感 FTP 站点启用加密传输（SFTP/FTPS）。作为安全基线，应停止使用已停止安全支持的 IE 版本，迁移至现代浏览器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ntbugtraq.ntadvice.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind9904&L=NTBUGTRAQ&P=R179","http://packetderm.cotse.com/mailing-lists/ntbugtraq/1999/0364.html","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3289","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19473","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1235","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1235.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-v7w3-r9q2-mwx4/GHSA-v7w3-r9q2-mwx4.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87772/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1235.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000751.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fe06dc37-1641-4571-a309-13ef3dac15ec.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1018.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0905","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1052","title":"Microsoft FrontPage 表单结果文件信息泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft FrontPage 默认将表单提交结果存储在网站根目录下的 `/_private/form_results.txt` 文件中，该文件权限设置为世界可读且位于 Web 文档根目录内，导致任何能够访问该网站的远程攻击者无需身份认证即可直接通过浏览器读取其他用户提交的敏感表单数据（如密码、个人信息等）。此漏洞危害中等，影响使用 Microsoft FrontPage 创建的网站。缓解措施包括更改默认存储路径或限制该文件的访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1052"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.350","remediation":"将 FrontPage 表单结果存储路径从默认的 `/_private/` 目录修改为 Web 根目录之外的路径（如 `C:\\fp_formdata\\`），并通过 IIS 权限设置拒绝匿名用户对 `form_results.txt` 的读取权限。如使用 Apache，在 `.htaccess` 中添加 `<FilesMatch \"form_results\\.txt\"> Deny from all</FilesMatch>` 规则。建议迁移至更新的 Web 开发平台（如 ASP.NET/PHP），因 FrontPage 已停止维护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93582550911564&w=2","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1052","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-1052.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch/GHSA-8552-5cm2-7wch.json","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88081/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1052.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0905.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0905.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0320","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0320.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0720","title":"GNU glibc pt_chown 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"GNU glibc 2.1/2.1.1 中的 pt_chown 辅助程序存在权限检查缺陷，该程序用于更改伪终端（PTY）设备的所有权，但未正确验证操作权限。本地攻击者可利用此漏洞修改属于其他用户的 TTY 终端设备，从而获取对其他用户终端的控制权，实现本地权限提升。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，无需其他特殊条件即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0720"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.947","remediation":"升级至 glibc 2.1.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 pt_chown 的 TTY 设备权限检查缺陷。如无法升级，可移除 pt_chown 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/libexec/pt_chown），或直接删除该二进制文件。现代 Linux 发行版已默认移除 pt_chown 组件，建议迁移至受支持的发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/597","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=lcamtuf.4.05.9907041223290.355-300000%40nimue.ids.pl","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19467","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/af5cedcf472f3690d94c4249ff35246f15692534/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0720.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0720","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0720.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ec31d5593e31331ed2058e001803e087d65aa416/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0720.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xcvw-xrwf-77hv/GHSA-xcvw-xrwf-77hv.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0720.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6fad8cd3-dc98-433e-82ae-44582e520fb1.json","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75d